   <taskbody>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Check that all transport units are attached to each other.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Lift the system to a location so that the bottom of the
sockets are accessible.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Attach the 4 corner adapter plates. Each corner plate is
attached with 2 countersunk M12 screws <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b> tightened to 65
Nm (48 lb-ft), and 2 hexagon socket head with serrated flange M12
screws <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b> tightened to 140 Nm (103 lb-ft).</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <note class="- topic/note ">The 2 countersunk M12 screws <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b> are on the edge
of the adapter plate facing either the front or the back of the system,
on the edges of the sockets.</note>
               <image href="../../Images/1230097_Wheels_Attatch_Adapter-plate_DD00732176.svg"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Attach the 4 middle adapter plates. Each middle plate is
attached with 4 hexagon socket head with serrated flange M12 screws <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b> tightened to 140 Nm (103 lb-ft).</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <image href="../../Images/1230097_Wheels_Attatch_Adapter-plate-middle_DD00737586.svg"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Attach the 8 wheels. Each wheel is attached on the adapter
plates with 4 hexagon socket head with serrated flange M8 screws <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(C)</b> tightened to 42 Nm (31 lb-ft).</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <image href="../../Images/1230097_Wheels_Attatch_Wheels_DD00732175.svg"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Check that all eight adapter plates and all eight wheels
are attached. Check that all screws are tightened to the specified
torque.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <image href="../../Images/1230097_Wheels_Locations_DD00732174.svg"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Lift the system so that it is standing on the wheels.</cmd>
         </step>
      </steps>
      <result class="- topic/section task/result ">The system can now be moved on wheels.</result>
